---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Installation">
  <h1>Installation</h1>

  <h2>Prerequisites</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Bun</strong> (v1.1+) — <a href="https://bun.sh">Install Bun</a></li>
    <li><strong>LLM Backend</strong> — Ollama (local) or OpenAI/Anthropic API key</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Install Agent Forge</h2>
  <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/yourusername/agent-forge.git
cd agent-forge
bun install</code></pre>

  <h2>Configure LLM Backend</h2>

  <h3>Ollama (Local, Default)</h3>
  <pre><code># Install Ollama from https://ollama.com
ollama pull llama3.2

# Verify
curl http://localhost:11434</code></pre>
  <p>Set base URL if different:</p>
  <pre><code>export OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434
export OLLAMA_MODEL=llama3.2</code></pre>

  <h3>OpenAI / Anthropic</h3>
  <pre><code>export OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
export OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o</code></pre>
  <p>Or use Anthropic:</p>
  <pre><code>export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
export OPENAI_MODEL=claude-3-5-sonnet-latest
export OPENAI_BASE_URL=https://api.anthropic.com/v1</code></pre>

  <h2>CLI Installation (Optional)</h2>
  <pre><code># Make CLI globally available
bun link

# Now use anywhere
agent-forge --help</code></pre>

  <h2>Verify Installation</h2>
  <pre><code>bun run src/cli.ts help</code></pre>
  <pre><code>agent-forge — Meta-framework for creating and auto-refining agents

Usage:
  agent-forge create <description>    Create and refine a new agent
  agent-forge list                    List all agents
  agent-forge history <name>         Show version history
  agent-forge inspect <name> [--v N]  Inspect agent code
  agent-forge help                   Show this help</code></pre>

  <h2>Project Structure</h2>
  <pre><code>agent-forge/
├── src/
│   ├── agent_schema.ts         # Agent file format
│   ├── generator.ts             # NL → agent code
│   ├── test_generator.ts        # Auto-generate test cases
│   ├── evaluator.ts             # Test runner + LLM judge
│   ├── refiner.ts              # Rewrite from failure report
│   ├── registry.ts              # SQLite persistence
│   ├── quality_gate.ts          # Pass/fail threshold
│   ├── loop_controller.ts       # Orchestration state machine
│   ├── runtime/
│   │   ├── executor.ts         # Single-agent execution
│   │   └── nested_executor.ts  # Multi-agent call graph
│   ├── llm_backend/            # Ollama / OpenAI adapters
│   └── output_adapters/        # Claude Skills / Standalone
└── docs/                        # This documentation site</code></pre>
</Layout>
